title: Get Your Laugh On Friday
itunes:title: Get Your Laugh On Friday
description:
Today on the show we had a friend to the room comedian Donnell Rawlings, and you know when he comes the jokes on him are always unfiltered. Also, we had comedian Ms. Pat stopped by, where she spoke about certain jokes she tells on stage, family support and more. Moreover, Charlamagne ended up giving rapper Logic "Donkey of the Day" after he called him out on a song.
